h3cTeTunnel.name: h3cTeTunnel
h3cTeTunnel.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
h3cTeTunnel.description: This MIB contains managed object definitions for the Multiprotocol Label Switching (MPLS) Te Tunnel.

h3cTeTunnelMaxTunnelIndex.name: h3cTeTunnelMaxTunnelIndex
h3cTeTunnelMaxTunnelIndex.description: The max value of tunnel id is permitted configure on the device.

h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspTable.name: h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspTable
h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspTable.description: This table contains information for static-crlsp, and through this to get detail information about this static-crlsp. Only support transit LSR and egress LSR.

h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspEntry.name: h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspEntry
h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspEntry.description: The entry in this table describes static-crlsp information.

h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspInLabel.name: h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspInLabel
h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspInLabel.description: This is unique label value that manualy assigned. Uniquely identifies a static-crlsp. Managers should use this to obtain detail static-crlsp information.

h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspName.name: h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspName
h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspName.description: The unique name assigned to the static-crlsp.

h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspStatus.name: h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspStatus
h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspStatus.description: Indicates the actual status of this static-crlsp, The value must be up when the static-crlsp status is up and the value must be down when the static-crlsp status is down.

h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspRole.name: h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspRole
h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspRole.description: This value indicate the role of this static-crlsp. This value must be transit at transit point of the tunnel, and tail at terminating point of the tunnel.

h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspXCPointer.name: h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspXCPointer
h3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspXCPointer.description: This pointer unique identify a row of mplsXCTable. This value should be zeroDotZero when the static-crlsp is down. The mplsXCTable identifies the segments that compose this tunnel, their characteristics, and relationships to each other.

h3cTeTunnelCoTable.name: h3cTeTunnelCoTable
h3cTeTunnelCoTable.description: This table contains information for Co-routed reverse crlsp and infomation of Co-routed bidirectional Tunnel Interface. If h3cCorouteTunnelLspInstance is zero, to obtain infomation of Co-routed bidirectional Tunnel Interface, otherwise to obtain Co-routed reverse crlsp infomation.

h3cTeTunnelCoEntry.name: h3cTeTunnelCoEntry
h3cTeTunnelCoEntry.description: The entry in this table describes Co-routed infomation of bidirectional Tunnel Interface and reserver lsp information.

h3cTeTunnelCoIndex.name: h3cTeTunnelCoIndex
h3cTeTunnelCoIndex.description: Uniquely identifies a set of tunnel instances between a pair of ingress and egress LSRs that specified at originating point. This value should be equal to the value signaled in the Tunnel Id of the Session object.

h3cTeTunnelCoLspInstance.name: h3cTeTunnelCoLspInstance
h3cTeTunnelCoLspInstance.description: When obtain infomation of Co-routed bidirectional Tunnel Interface, this vlaue should be zero. And this value must be LspID to obtain reverse crlsp information. Values greater than 0, but less than or equal to 65535, should be useless.

h3cTeTunnelCoIngressLSRId.name: h3cTeTunnelCoIngressLSRId
h3cTeTunnelCoIngressLSRId.description: Identity the ingress LSR associated with this tunnel instance. This vlaue is equal to the LsrID of originating endpoint.

h3cTeTunnelCoEgressLSRId.name: h3cTeTunnelCoEgressLSRId
h3cTeTunnelCoEgressLSRId.description: Identity of the egress LSR associated with this tunnel instance. This vlaue is equal to the LsrID of terminating point.

h3cTeTunnelCoBiMode.name: h3cTeTunnelCoBiMode
h3cTeTunnelCoBiMode.description: This vlaue indicated the bidirection mode of tunnel interface. The valuemust be coroutedActive at the originating point of the tunnel and coroutedPassive at the terminating point.

h3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspInstance.name: h3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspInstance
h3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspInstance.description: This value indicated the reverse lsp instance, and should be equal to obverse lsp instance.

h3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspXCPointer.name: h3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspXCPointer
h3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspXCPointer.description: This pointer unique index to mplsXCTable of the reverse lsp. The mplsXCTable identifies the segments that compose this tunnel, their characteristics, and relationships to each other. A value of zeroDotZero indicate that there is no crlsp assigned to this.

h3cTeTunnelPsTable.name: h3cTeTunnelPsTable
h3cTeTunnelPsTable.description: This table defines some objects for managers to obtain TE tunnel Protection Switching group current status information.

h3cTeTunnelPsEntry.name: h3cTeTunnelPsEntry
h3cTeTunnelPsEntry.description: The entry in this table describes TE tunnel Protection Switching group infromation.

h3cTeTunnelPsIndex.name: h3cTeTunnelPsIndex
h3cTeTunnelPsIndex.description: Uniquely identifies a TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance. This value must be equal to the tunnel id of work tunnel instance.

h3cTeTunnelPsIngressLSRId.name: h3cTeTunnelPsIngressLSRId
h3cTeTunnelPsIngressLSRId.description: Identity the ingress LSR associated with work tunnel instance.

h3cTeTunnelPsEgressLSRId.name: h3cTeTunnelPsEgressLSRId
h3cTeTunnelPsEgressLSRId.description: Identity of the egress LSR associated with work tunnel instance.

h3cTeTunnelPsProtectIndex.name: h3cTeTunnelPsProtectIndex
h3cTeTunnelPsProtectIndex.description: Uniquely identifies a TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance. This value must be equal to the tunnel id of TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance.

h3cTeTunnelPsProtectIngressLSRId.name: h3cTeTunnelPsProtectIngressLSRId
h3cTeTunnelPsProtectIngressLSRId.description: Identity the ingress LSR associated with TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance.

h3cTeTunnelPsProtectEgressLSRId.name: h3cTeTunnelPsProtectEgressLSRId
h3cTeTunnelPsProtectEgressLSRId.description: Identity of the egress LSR associated with TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance.

h3cTeTunnelPsProtectType.name: h3cTeTunnelPsProtectType
h3cTeTunnelPsProtectType.description: This value indicated TE tunnel Protection Switching group type. The default value is oneToOne.

h3cTeTunnelPsRevertiveMode.name: h3cTeTunnelPsRevertiveMode
h3cTeTunnelPsRevertiveMode.description: This value indicated protect switch mode. The value must be revertive or nonRevertive, default value is revertive.

h3cTeTunnelPsWtrTime.name: h3cTeTunnelPsWtrTime
h3cTeTunnelPsWtrTime.description: The cycle time that switch to protect tunnel.

h3cTeTunnelPsHoldOffTime.name: h3cTeTunnelPsHoldOffTime
h3cTeTunnelPsHoldOffTime.description: This value is switchback delay time. When detected the work path fault, switch to protect path after this time.

h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchMode.name: h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchMode
h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchMode.description: This value indicated TE tunnel Protection Switching group switch mode.

h3cTeTunnelPsWorkPathStatus.name: h3cTeTunnelPsWorkPathStatus
h3cTeTunnelPsWorkPathStatus.description: This value indicates work path status. none, noDefect, inDefect will be used.

h3cTeTunnelPsProtectPathStatus.name: h3cTeTunnelPsProtectPathStatus
h3cTeTunnelPsProtectPathStatus.description: This value indicates protect path status. none, noDefect, inDefect(3) will be used.

h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchResult.name: h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchResult
h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchResult.description: This value indicated current using path is work path or protect path.

h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchWtoP.name: h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchWtoP
h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchWtoP.description: This notification is generated when protect workgroup switch from work tunnel to protect tunnel.

h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchPtoW.name: h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchPtoW
h3cTeTunnelPsSwitchPtoW.description: This notification is generated when protect workgroup switch from protect tunnel to work tunnel.

h3cTeTunnelNotificationsGroup.name: h3cTeTunnelNotificationsGroup
h3cTeTunnelNotificationsGroup.description: This group contains MPLS Te Tunnel traps.

h3cTeTunnelScalarsGroup.name: h3cTeTunnelScalarsGroup
h3cTeTunnelScalarsGroup.description: Scalar object needed to implement MPLS te tunnels.

h3cTeTunnelCorouteGroup.name: h3cTeTunnelCorouteGroup
h3cTeTunnelCorouteGroup.description: Objects for quering Co-routed reverse crlsp information.

h3cTeTunnelPsGroup.name: h3cTeTunnelPsGroup
h3cTeTunnelPsGroup.description: Objects for quering protect workgroup information.
